A state of lightness in seems to be
===================================
In out day to day life we feel many things and when we feel that time it seems to be/look like right/wrong, faithful/ harmful..ie some thing left or right.

Normally whatever we feel that is injected/added in our experiences for further life and the same one take lead in similar situation, We  realize many times the same experience work and some time the same one fail out for resolution of some scenario.
When we get strong feeling/seems to be then we capture this feeling for long time and thinking it right/right for at least me.

***Feeling by using interface of mind is nothing but seems to be***

Whatever we feel even using interface of mind or observation that exists for you only in that moment of time. It may change latter diminish/improve depends up your approach/angle of perceiving towards scenario later.
But when we feel better then we try to carry for further journey and when we feel bad then we try to leave at that moment. But the same one feeling neither left that time or not it get carry long time for further journey since this is kept in our memory because of poor understanding.
We unable to think this is just a state during journey this is neither for carry in further nor to leave there.

***Carry in observation is a experience and carry in mind is a lust***
Ex-
When you are on non returning journey and you look many things like valley of flower,adventurous heal,adventurous birds/animals/water fall..so on, If you are a observer you not only enjoy to look these things but also you look inside the creation of these things since you realize this is in instance and whatever come next will be also excited for that instance you never concentrate to carry in memory.
But when you walk only through mind/senses you will not only look these things but you will also carry this in strong memory since later you will have use for imagination and feel good, you don't have realization that next moment will also come for some purpose and that will be also excite in different ways but you concentrate to carry.

When our mind try to enjoy by looking and same time it try to carry for further then the same energy/attention get distributed in two direction one for enjoy and other for carry the stuff, in that situation we neither enjoy that moment nor carry in well ways.

When we realize it is not possible to carry the scenario in some moment in our memory for future journey since that scenario has over in that moment only and the one
new will come might be look like similar but moment will must be different and we need to look by new ways of observation then your concentration always on the cream part of
scenario ie the internal structure of waves that perceive during scenario.
With that understanding we don't get attach with what seems to be now, we understand whatever we seems to be is for that moment and it can't be carry out.
This is nothing but lightness in seems to be.

***Observation only hold the structures of waves where as mind keep the hole scenario as much possible***
***Observation is a proxy type reference but mind keep in memory of hole object/scenario***
***Observation get injected in invisible energy by default where as remembering not simply get injected in our memory but our lust help it to inject n memory***

